headline: Dollar Could Fall Sharply if U.S. Jobs Data Miss Forecasts
summary: The dollar strengthened, but could fall sharply if the U.S. nonfarm payrolls report on Friday misses expectations, Ebury said.

headline: Canadian Dollar Rises After Reports PM Trudeau Could Resign
summary: The Canadian dollar rose following media reports that Prime Minister Justin Trudeau could announce that he will resign, potentially as early as Monday.
